  "slug": "ender-sender",
  "title": "Ender Sender: Remote Block Depot",
  "description": "A mod which lets you move items straight to your inventory as you use them up, coming from a special kind of chest.",
  "body": "<p>A mod which lets you move items straight to your inventory as you use them up, coming from a special kind of chest.</p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PNshlbc.png\" alt=\"Banner\" width=\"682\" height=\"392\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3LsbORI.png\" alt=\"Ender Sender is a mod by Rasa Novum which gives players the power to refill their inventory as they place blocks. No need to go back-and-forth!\" width=\"1024\" height=\"515\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CtUnk6c.gif\" alt=\"Animated GIF of blocks being placed while the inventory is refilled\" width=\"660\" height=\"371\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gVP0cc9.png\" alt=\"The Ender Sender acts as a storage block where you can add blocks you want to be refilled. Connect the Ender Sender to a hopper for automation or even more storage!\" width=\"1200\" height=\"525\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LsDSX2e.png\" alt=\"You will always connect to the closest non-empty Ender Sender within range. When you connect or disconnect to the Ender Sender, you will be alerted with a client-side visual and audio cue.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"630\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/akyKhoL.png\" alt=\"Crafting Recipe (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KgloJp6.png\" alt=\"The crafting recipe\" width=\"1024\" height=\"528\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/BgIG2ey.png\" alt=\"Gamerules (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VVLuqx2.png\" alt=\"You can adjust settings for Ender Sender in-game with gamerules: gamerule enderSenderRange number (Sets the effective range of the Ender Sender, the number of blocks away you can be while staying connected) gamerule doEnderSenderEffects true or false (Determines whether the client-side audio and visual cues for connection and disconnection play) Note that gamerules affect all players in a world\" width=\"1024\" height=\"515\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/JF0tgUl.png\" alt=\"FAQ (Title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the default range of the Ender Sender?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">The default range is within 32 blocks of the Ender Sender (translates to a 64x64x64 cube).</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Will there be a Fabric port?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">We're looking into it, but there's nothing in the works yet.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Will this mod be available for version X?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jLQd2vq.png\" alt=\"idk\" width=\"285\" height=\"113\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Are there any planned features?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">The door is always open, but there's nothing planned at the moment.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">What do I do if my Ender Sender has thoughts and feelings independent of my own?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Please terminate the game and leave an issue on our Github immediately.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Can I use this in my modpack and/or server?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Yes, as long as it's downloaded from our official sources.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">What is Rasa Novum?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">We're a small group of mostly amateur developers making mods for our modpack and eventual server of the same name.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">If you have any bug reports, please leave them on our <a href=\"https://github.com/RasaNovum/Ender_Sender/issues\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Issue Tracker</a>.</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDMrvJs.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/rqpXHrJ.png\" alt=\"Socials (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.rasanovum.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dWKubWd.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/WGh4mq6W5U\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iGKNGA3.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/RasaNovum\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0gYQeJT.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Rasa_Novum\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5h47qoo.png\" width=\"117\" height=\"96\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">If you're a fan of tightly designed mods like Ender Sender, try checking out our other mods for building and infrastructure like Timber Frames and Via Romana!</p>",
